p.d: As you would have seen already, our Evangelical Christian, Tiffany, had been turned to the Dark Side by Lara some time ago and now it was the turn of Jim Slip to lead her onto the path of wickedness and depravity! She even sank to the depths of inviting Lara to join us in some crazed 3 some xxx madness!
